textMap.PRIMARY: You've Got To Change Your Way of Loving
You've Got To Change Your Way of Loving
Daniel Roebuck: Bears a slight resemblance to actor Lee Majors II, son of The Six Million Dollar Man (1974) star Lee Majors.

Rufus Sewell: His father, Bill Sewell, an animator, employed an impressionistic approach to Rotoscoping - the technique of tracing over film negatives - in his own film "Half in Love with Fred Astaire" and then in the famous "Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds" sequence in "Yellow Submarine.".

Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa: On July 09, 2010, Cary participated in the All-Russia Channel 1 evening TV-show "Let's Marry" as lead character in search of a wife. He successfully selected a beautiful 23-year old Russian bride out of 3 preselected candidates. They were both happy to meet each other.
Alexa Davalos: She is the daughter of actress Elyssa Davalos.
